{"id":9536,"content":"<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">《炎黄春秋》杂志已分别在搜狐新闻、网易新闻、新浪新闻等客户端开通文章发布平台，以<SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">方便读者手机阅读</SPAN>。与炎黄春秋纸样版有所不同的是，手机阅读将会看到《炎黄春秋》杂志</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%\"><FONT face=Calibri>1991</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年创刊以来公开发表的多篇精彩文章，这些早期文章在纸刊上已难寻觅，是弥足珍贵的史料。《炎黄春秋》杂志这些早期文章将与最新文章穿插着在手机阅读中为读者提供。<BR></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">　　手机阅读方式：在手机上安装上述新闻软件，打开新闻软件后，点击“订阅”，从中选取“炎黄春秋”即完成订阅过程。（<FONT face=楷体>炎黄春秋在手机上的文章均免费阅读</FONT>）<BR><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <BR>　　<FONT face=黑体>图示：<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp; </P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=center><IMG style=\"HEIGHT: 348px; WIDTH: 319px\" border=0 alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.yhcqw.com/upFiles/czhang2014tubian/2014063016184512111.jpg\" width=28 height=32></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=center><BR>在手机上下载并安装搜狐（网易、新浪）新闻软件<BR><BR><BR><IMG style=\"HEIGHT: 356px; WIDTH: 262px\" border=0 alt=\"\" src=\"/upFiles/czhang2014tubian/2014063016194514782.jpg\" width=518 height=691><IMG style=\"HEIGHT: 349px; WIDTH: 285px\" border=0 alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.yhcqw.com/upFiles/czhang2014tubian/2014063016194592755.jpg\" width=28 height=32><BR>选择“炎黄春秋”订阅<BR><BR><BR>以下为炎黄春秋早期文章与最新文章发布在手机上的截图<BR></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=center><IMG style=\"HEIGHT: 394px; WIDTH: 304px\" border=0 alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.yhcqw.com/upFiles/czhang2014tubian/20140630161845848.jpg\" width=28 height=32></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=center><IMG style=\"HEIGHT: 436px; WIDTH: 294px\" border=0 alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.yhcqw.com/upFiles/czhang2014tubian/2014063016194532277.jpg\" width=28 height=32><BR></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=center><IMG style=\"HEIGHT: 402px; WIDTH: 486px\" border=0 alt=\"\" src=\"/upFiles/czhang2014tubian/201406301618459134.jpg\" width=1037 height=778></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=left>&nbsp;</P></FONT></SPAN></SPAN>","title":"炎黄春秋手机阅读方式介绍","time":1404060386999}